# Linux 环境部署

## Python：
+ python3 pip：`sudo apt-get install python3-pip`
+ pyqtgraph:[deb](http://pyqtgraph.org/)  `sudo dpkg ***.deb --install`

## Leap Motion
+ Check Leap Motion daemon with:`service leapd status`
+ Open the Leap Motion GUI with:`LeapControlPanel`

+ + `echo "export PYTHONPATH=$PYTHONPATH:/home/shuixin/Downloads/LeapDeveloperKit/LeapSDK/lib:/home/shuixin/Downloads/LeapDeveloperKit/LeapSDK/lib/x64" >> ~/.bashrc`
  + `source ~/.bashrc`
